cat << EOF
This project is a linux driver that allow owners of Asus laptops to
use all the functionalities of their computer such as special keys,
special LEDs, control of brightness, ... this project is included in
the linux kernel (from 2.4.22).

You'll need to build the kernel module yourself... (it's in 2.4.22
and 2.6)
EOF
